    "description": "进入 Mini Sports 的世界，这是一款提供多种 1 对 1 小游戏的在线游戏。挑战来自世界各地的玩家，或邀请你的朋友与你一起在经典有趣的游戏中竞争，如 8 球池、赛车、羽毛球、冰壶、迷你高尔夫和射箭。<br><br><strong>🎱 8 球池</strong><br>经典的台球游戏，玩家轮流将所有球击入球袋。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/5b4840d4784c86653e89a01a9106e609.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏎️ 赛车</strong><br>在一场比赛中竞争，最快完成圈数的玩家获胜。使用熟练的驾驶技巧在赛道上导航并击败你的对手。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/ca5dc96060cb95b47856cda2439df7cc.mp4?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🏸 羽毛球</strong><br>基本上是网球，但使用羽毛球代替球。将羽毛球送到对手的一边并赢得分数。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.poster.avif?t=1740838151\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335250/extras/df46422c4d17b6c2e483bdeccd50d8ea.webm?t=1740838151\" type=\"video/webm; 